  "title": "Receptionist cum Admin (Part Time)",
  "description": "<p>Job Description & Requirements</p><p>We are looking for a receptionist to be responsible for being the face of the office - greeting clients and visitors and general admin duty. You will be in charge of contacting employees regarding visitors, answering phones and taking messages, and sorting and distributing mail.</p><p>The candidate will need the following: </p><ul><li>Flexibility is essential, as well as a willingness to assist with tasks.</li><li>Help solve unforeseen problems, answer queries etc. </li><li>Good communication is an essential attribute as we will supporting an office of various nationalities.</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>ROLES & RESPONSIBILITIES</strong></p><ul><li>Managing the reception, answering incoming calls, and transferring calls to relevant personnel appropriately</li><li>Attending to walk-in customers and directing them to the relevant staff.</li><li>Meet and greet visitors and notify appropriate staff of their arrival.</li><li>Maintaining reception area is tidy and presentable, with all necessary stationery and material (e.g. pens, forms).</li><li>Some Administrative work & Data entry and updating databases.</li><li>Handle courier, postal, and dispatch activities.</li><li>Assist management with basic admin tasks.</li><li>Handle day-to-day office administration.\n\n</li></ul>",
